<center>
<div class="main">
Ajax Pages is a scripting template engine that enables rapid
development of Ajax Web-based Applications, just like <a
 href="http://mail.google.com/">GMail</a>,
<a href="http://maps.google.com/">Google
Maps</a>, <a href="http://www.backpackit.com/">A9</a>
and <a href="http://www.backpackit.com/">Backpack</a>,
but without having to
manipulate
complicated&nbsp;Document Object Models to make things dynamic.<br>
<br>
Based on the experience of JSP, ASP and PHP, Ajax Pages brings easy
scripting templates to the client-side. Anyone familiar with these
tecnologies will feel at home with Ajax Pages.<br>
<br>
Ajax Pages has been tested on Firefox, Internet Explorer and Opera and
works&nbsp;well on all of them. Right now, Ajax Pages is pretty
much
usable
and stable, although it is still in beta stage.<br>
<br>
If your already familiar with Javascript, take <a
 href="doc/5_min_tutorial.html">our five minutes
tutorial</a> and get to know what
Ajax Pages can do for you.<br>
</div>
</center>
